33:24.698 --> 33:27.875
- One text from Jennifer
to Mei Shen.

33:32.053 --> 33:33.489
- Address in Queens.

33:34.969 --> 33:37.058
- He said
she's on the third floor.

33:37.102 --> 33:40.409
Her name's Mei Shen.

33:40.453 --> 33:43.021
- This gotta be her apartment.

33:43.064 --> 33:44.065
- Oh.
- Call a bus!

33:44.109 --> 33:45.458
- Yep. Got it.

33:45.501 --> 33:52.639
