33:56.208 --> 33:56.382
.

33:56.425 --> 33:58.862
- According to the shelter,
Mei had been in the States

33:58.906 --> 34:00.386
a couple months.
No visa, no paper trail.

34:00.429 --> 34:02.083
- Family back in China?

34:02.127 --> 34:03.998
- Well, only Jennifer Lee
can answer that for us.

34:04.042 --> 34:06.174
- She was likely smuggled in
and paying off her debts.

34:06.218 --> 34:07.436
- No way she was
doing that at a bank.

34:07.480 --> 34:09.090
It must have been a cover.
- Ballistics.

34:09.134 --> 34:11.310
Bullet that killed Mei Shen
matches the markings

34:11.353 --> 34:13.094
on the bullet that
hit Jennifer Lee.

34:13.138 --> 34:14.791
- Okay, so we have two women
gunned down,

34:14.835 --> 34:18.404
one weapon, two gangs beefing,

34:18.447 --> 34:20.188
and a global bank?

34:20.232 --> 34:22.712
- I can try to pull together
a list of the bank's clients.

34:22.755 --> 34:24.018
- To try and find a pattern.

34:24.062 --> 34:25.889
[phone chimes]
Good idea.

34:25.933 --> 34:27.804
Everything all right?

34:27.848 --> 34:30.068
- It's a text from Captain Lin.

34:30.110 --> 34:31.721
The 4th is making a move.

34:31.764 --> 34:34.724
[tense music]

34:34.768 --> 34:37.074
