35:32.695 --> 35:35.481
- Thank you for the
stellar work, Captain Lin.

35:35.524 --> 35:37.178
- We had an agreement.

35:37.222 --> 35:38.614
You did not loop us in.

35:38.658 --> 35:39.963
- Tip came in.

35:40.007 --> 35:41.965
- Captain Lin called.
We had to act fast.

35:42.009 --> 35:43.967
- We recovered the gun
from Yuze's office.

35:44.011 --> 35:45.404
His prints are all over it.

35:45.447 --> 35:47.145
Yuze's our shooter.

35:47.188 --> 35:49.059
- Hey, we're all on the
same team here, remember?

35:49.103 --> 35:50.931
This is a win for all of us.

35:50.974 --> 35:52.237
- Don't worry.

35:52.280 --> 35:54.500
Your squad can take
all the credit.

35:54.543 --> 35:56.458
You brought Yuze in.
You have him in custody.

35:56.502 --> 35:58.982
- There is one issue
with your victory lap.

35:59.026 --> 36:00.984
We picked up Yuze 24 hours ago.

36:01.028 --> 36:03.900
- Clearly, he paid a visit to
Mei before you picked him up.

36:03.944 --> 36:05.685
- No. Body was warm.

36:05.728 --> 36:07.121
Blood on the floor fresh.

36:07.165 --> 36:09.732
He couldn't have shot Mei.

36:09.776 --> 36:12.344
- Look, we got him.

36:12.387 --> 36:13.606
It's done.

36:13.649 --> 36:15.521
- So forget the details.
Just go for the win.

36:17.218 --> 36:18.698
- Look, stick around
for the press conference.

36:18.741 --> 36:22.484
I wanna give you guys
a special acknowledgment, yeah?

36:22.528 --> 36:24.573
- Have you notified
Stephen Lee?

36:24.617 --> 36:25.922
- His wife woke up today.

36:25.966 --> 36:27.185
He's staying with her
at the hospital.

36:29.622 --> 36:30.579
- You buying any of this?

36:30.623 --> 36:32.233
- Not for a second.

36:35.367 --> 36:38.326
- Chrysanthemums, my favorite.

36:38.370 --> 36:41.155
In Chinese culture,
they symbolize

36:41.199 --> 36:43.679
longevity and vitality.

36:43.723 --> 36:45.072
- Words to live by.

36:45.115 --> 36:46.726
- It's nice to finally
meet you, Ms. Lee.

36:46.769 --> 36:48.771
- Jennifer, please.

36:48.815 --> 36:50.382
And I can't thank you enough

36:50.425 --> 36:51.948
for all that you've done
for us.

36:51.992 --> 36:54.255
- Oh, no need for thanks.

36:54.299 --> 36:56.953
We're just happy you're okay.

36:56.997 --> 36:58.781
What's next for you two?

36:58.825 --> 37:02.350
- We will find new ways
to serve our community.

37:02.394 --> 37:06.311
My only focus right now
is getting her home.

37:06.354 --> 37:08.269
- Honey, press conference.
- Oh, yes.

37:08.313 --> 37:10.184
- Before it starts, we just
have a few questions for you,

37:10.228 --> 37:11.185
if you don't mind.

37:11.229 --> 37:12.578
- Regarding Mei Shen.

37:13.927 --> 37:15.102
- What about Mei?

37:16.930 --> 37:20.368
- I'm really sorry to tell you
this, but Mei was murdered.

37:20.412 --> 37:22.544
- What?

37:22.588 --> 37:23.893
What happened? When?

37:23.937 --> 37:26.026
- During your recovery.

37:26.069 --> 37:27.680
Now, I'm hoping you'll
be able to help us

37:27.723 --> 37:29.595
figure out who's responsible.

37:29.638 --> 37:31.249
[suspenseful music]

37:31.292 --> 37:33.555
- Maybe this isn't a good time.

37:33.599 --> 37:35.122
- No.

37:35.165 --> 37:36.732
How can I help?

37:36.776 --> 37:40.736
- Well, Mei was staying at your
shelter, and then she left.

37:40.780 --> 37:41.694
Any idea why?

37:43.696 --> 37:47.090
- She was indebted
to some scary people.

37:47.134 --> 37:48.875
She didn't wanna
bring any danger

37:48.918 --> 37:51.181
to the other girls
at the shelter.

37:51.225 --> 37:52.705
I begged her to stay.

37:54.489 --> 37:57.318
When she didn't,
I asked Michael

37:57.362 --> 37:59.407
to help her get a safe place
outside of Chinatown.

37:59.451 --> 38:01.235
- And that would
be Michael Quan.

38:01.279 --> 38:03.759
- Yeah, he's always
been there for us.

38:03.803 --> 38:05.413
It's starting.

38:05.457 --> 38:08.286
- The NYPD remains confident
that we will bring

38:08.329 --> 38:10.418
Jennifer Lee's shooter
to justice.

38:10.462 --> 38:12.899
As a personal friend
of Mr. and Mrs. Lee's,

38:12.942 --> 38:16.729
I'm here to introduce
the very fine Michael Quan.

38:16.772 --> 38:18.557
- Thank you.

38:18.600 --> 38:21.299
Hello, everyone. Um.

38:21.342 --> 38:25.390
Mr. and Mrs. Lee asked me
to speak on their behalf.

38:25.433 --> 38:29.524
Mr. Lee has decided to withdraw
from the race at this time

38:29.568 --> 38:32.788
to focus
on his wife's recovery.

38:32.832 --> 38:36.226
I have decided to honor
my friend Stephen Lee

38:36.270 --> 38:40.796
by taking his place
in the race for councilman.

38:40.840 --> 38:43.059
I will be running
on the same platform

38:43.103 --> 38:44.713
that Stephen and Jennifer

38:44.757 --> 38:48.151
have committed their lives to.
[phone buzzes]

38:48.195 --> 38:49.588
- Yeah, Jet.

38:49.631 --> 38:52.330
- I did a dive into Stephen
Lee's campaign finances.

38:52.373 --> 38:54.549
Contributions were made
by an LLC

38:54.593 --> 38:56.682
linked to an international
shipping company.

38:56.725 --> 38:58.814
That company was implicated
two years ago

38:58.858 --> 39:02.775
in a human trafficking
operation out of China.

39:02.818 --> 39:05.734
And you'll never guess who's
on the board of directors.

39:05.778 --> 39:07.432
- Michael Quan.

39:07.475 --> 39:11.044
- I promise you, I will work
as hard as I can every day.

39:11.087 --> 39:12.088
- Jet, let me get back to you.

39:12.132 --> 39:13.742
Sarge?

39:13.786 --> 39:16.266
- Yeah. Um, excuse us.

39:19.618 --> 39:21.533
- Jet.

39:21.576 --> 39:25.537
Quan financed Lee's campaign.
All of it with dirty money.

39:26.755 --> 39:29.802
He's the one
behind the trafficking.

39:29.845 --> 39:33.893
- So he's the one that needed
Jennifer Lee out of the way.

39:33.936 --> 39:35.851
- All roads lead to Quan.

39:35.895 --> 39:39.072
[tense music]

39:39.115 --> 39:40.682
- Extra security
at my home and offices,

39:40.726 --> 39:43.990
and schedule all
press appearances remotely.

39:44.033 --> 39:45.774
- Mr. Quan.

39:45.818 --> 39:48.386
Can I have a word with you?
In private?

39:48.429 --> 39:51.519
- Uh...thank you, everyone.

39:51.563 --> 39:53.303
Detective.

39:53.347 --> 39:55.262
Are you here
to endorse my campaign?

39:55.305 --> 39:59.397
- No, no, no, I'm here
to make a promise and, uh,

39:59.440 --> 40:02.704
have a heart-to-heart with you.

40:02.748 --> 40:04.271
- About what?

40:05.838 --> 40:08.406
- Well, you and I both know
that, uh, you're responsible

40:08.449 --> 40:11.147
for the attempted murder
of Jennifer Lee.

40:12.975 --> 40:15.282
That's the heart-to-heart.

40:15.325 --> 40:17.110
Here's the promise.

40:18.416 --> 40:20.896
You will go down for it.

